:

1. *Bacio* je nju u lice i otišao. (He kissed her on the face and left.)
2. Ona mu je *bacila* oko za vreme časa. (She cast him a glance during the lesson.)
3. On je *bacio* preko ramena pogled na mene. (He threw a glance over his shoulder at me.)
4. *Bacio* je novac u fontanu. (He threw money in the fountain.)
5. Ona je *bačena* u zatvor. (She was thrown into prison.)